  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\" property=\"schema:text\"><p> </p><p>The recently concluded IIS Global Insurance Forum (GIF) in Singapore yielded, as our annual conference always does, some interesting insights into the major trends in the industry. One of the most striking developments in the international insurance business was evident at the Forum: the dramatic growth of Asia’s stature and role in<br/>prospective growth.</p><p><br/><a href=\"/sites/default/files/2019-07/Insights%20July%202019.pdf\"><strong>Learn More</strong></a><strong> &gt;</strong><br/> </p></div></body></html>",
